<p class="p">Based on the MEM and the fuzzy mathematics, membership functions were calculated to obtain the values of all factors and units, while the weights were obtained from the MEM. Then, the weighted average method [Eq. 
 <xref ref-type="disp-formula" rid="eqn-4" class="xref">(4)</xref>] was used to comprehensively assess the values of
 <italic class="italic"> S. sphenanthera</italic> ecological suitability in the study area (
 <xref rid="ref-30" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">Lu et al., 2012</xref>; 
 <xref rid="ref-17" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">Guo et al., 2013</xref>). 
